Store Introduction
This is Auto Equip Rental Shop. The [i.imgur.com] license from Tenboro

Description
During testing, unexpected situations may still arise. If you encounter any issues, please PM/MM ericeric91.

Rules and Features
  • The Equip in this store will never be sold. Multiple inquiries will be considered harassment and will be reported to Mod.
  • Take responsibility for your own credit and accountability within your community.
  • Strictly prohibited to relend or resell.
  • Rental Conditions:
    • A maximum of 7 pieces of equipment could be rented by the same person at the same time, if you want to rent more, return your rented equipment first.
    • Longest rental period is 7 days.
    • The same equipment can be rented up to 3 times.
    • All rental fees are in persistent credits.
    • You are not allowed to rent a equipment that is over your current level.
    • When returning equipment, return it through MM to HVEquipRental, and do not set CoD.
    • Allow enhancement forging for rental equipment.
    • Allow upgrading equipment below IW10 to IW10.
    • Equipment at IW10 is prohibited from being reforged.
  • Return Instructions:
    • Return it through MM to HVEquipRental, and do not set CoD.
    • Allow multiple pieces of equipment to be attached in one MM.
    • After receiving the equipment, HVEquipRental will calculate the return time and refund a portion of the rental fee.
    • If the returned equipment is returned to ericeric91 by mistake, a 10% service fee will be charged.
  • When a rented item is returned:
    • If it's rental period has not expired, 80% of the fee would be refunded.
    • If overdue for 3 days, 60% of the fee would be refunded.
    • If overdue for 5 days, 40% of the fee would be refunded.
    • If overdue for 7 days, 20% of the fee would be refunded.
    • If overdue for more than 7 days, there would be no refund.
  • Format for Renting:
    • Please use the equipment ID and integer day when asking for any equipment.
    • Multiple equipment items can be called in the same response.
    • You are not allowed to edit your post, edited posts will be ignored by the bot.
    • The incorrect calling number format, conditions, and quantity will be listed #6.
    • Here are the acceptable ways:

中文規則與說明
  • 此商店的裝備永遠不會售出，多次詢問者將視為騷擾行為，將回報 Mod 處理
  • 請對自己的信用負責，以及對自己的社群負責
  • 嚴禁轉借、轉賣行為
  • 租借事項：
    • 最多可以同時借用 7 件裝備
    • 最長可以借用 7 天
    • 同件裝備最多可租借 3 次
    • 所有租借都是使用 Persistent Credits
    • 租借叫號時，等級不得低於裝備等級
    • 允許對裝備做加強鍛造
    • 允許將未滿 IW10 的裝備，提升至 IW10
    • IW10 裝備，禁止 Reforge
  • 歸還事項：
    • 將裝備透過 MM 歸還至 HVEquipRental，且不得設定 CoD
    • 允許在一個 MM 中附上多件裝備
    • HVEquipRental 收到裝備後，將會計算歸還時間，並退回部分租金
    • 若歸還裝備錯誤的退還給 ericeric91，會收 1 成服務費
  • 歸還退回金額：
    • 期限內歸還將退回 80%
    • 超過期限但未滿 3 天將退回 60%
    • 超過期限 3 天未滿 5 天將退回 40%
    • 超過期限 5 天未滿 7 天將退回 20%
    • 超過期限 7 天以上不退費
  • 叫號事項：
    • 叫號使用 Equip ID、整數天份
    • 可以在同一個回應中，對多件裝備叫號
    • 叫號的帖子不能編輯，否則將忽略訂單

[English]
This service is "want to buy" equipment , Not "want to sell".
The purchase price is currently set at 5 times the system store price.
Contact ericeric91 for MM purchases

Tentative guide to renting equipment：
    1H
  • Only Rapier.
  • Weapons must have the suffix "Slaughter."
    • For levels 100 to 250, the minimum required quality is Exquisite.
    • For levels 251 to 350, the minimum required quality is Magnificent.
    Shield
  • Only Force Shield.
    • For levels 100 to 250, the minimum required quality is Exquisite.
    • For levels 251 to 350, the minimum required quality is Magnificent.
    Light
    • Light No condition at the moment.
    Heavy
  • Power is best.
    • For levels 100 to 250, the minimum required quality is Exquisite.
    • For levels 251 to 350, the minimum required quality is Magnificent.
  • Plate armor requires higher quality.
    • For levels 100 to 200, the minimum required quality is Magnificent , and it must also have the 'shielding' prefix.
    • For levels 201 to 250, the minimum required quality is Legendary , and it must also have the 'shielding' prefix.
    Cloth
    • This store does not rent Cloth
Donation Conditions:
To reduce the quality requirements for purchases by one level, for example: Legendary will be downgraded to Magnificent.
The level cap has been extended to below 400 to prevent the continuous accumulation of ineffective equipment.
Equipment below level 100, sup quality rapier of slaughter is an exception.
MM given to this store will be automatically accepted, and records will be retained.

If there are any questions about the rules, please contact the store administrator ericeric91
